snippet.title: Teeto - Gameplay Trailer - November 2024
snippet.description:
Spyro the Dragon meets Kirby in this absolutely adorable adventure 3D platformer.

Play as a tiny blob and bunny duo, traversing the big wide world on their epic adventure. 

Use Teeto's special ability of being able to absorb different elements and objects from the environment. 

Battle shadow monsters, explore and collect, and help out the cast of crazy characters you meet along the way.

Play the demo and wishlist our game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2783370/Teeto/
